TargetFactor_Question:

(option a) - Belief
(option b) - Attitude
(option c) - Costs
(option d) - Threat severity
TargetFactor_Response:

Strengthening the attitude towards information security compliance is crucial. While Samantha Jones already values company policies and focuses on safeguarding data, Emma Garcia exhibits a tendency to break rules when they believe there are no consequences. By targeting and improving the attitude towards consistently following policies, regardless of perceived consequences, employees like Emma Garcia can be encouraged to adhere to information security rules more diligently.
